{"tid":1906083,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[黃色經濟圈] 身為黃店可唔可以播返多啲抗爭相關歌曲","createTime":"2020-03-01T16:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T09:26:55.000Z","uid":38737,"like":22,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"2d3f2b4412611cd363df54f0d0842606de430937","tid":1906083,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"呢幾日去過幾間幾出名嘅黃店<br />\n海報 文宣 memo紙 咩都有齊<br />\n唯獨好似缺少同呢場抗爭/革命有關嘅歌<br />\n唔知係咪只係因為我聽唔到<br />\n定因為抗爭耐咗而冇咗呢樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食得黃店唔會係因為啲嘢好好食 亦都唔奢求<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係希望將抗爭再融入生活<br />\n幫襯時同時有視覺同<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽覺</span></strong>嘅滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如果黃店腦細/職員睇到<br />\n希望你地播返多啲抗爭歌（原創/二創）<br />\n唔係點襯得起黃店之名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔知有咩歌唔緊要<br />\n下面我list埋俾你<br />\n未能盡錄 以作參考<br />\n自行去youtube download<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港 (不同版本）<br />\n<br />\n不屈進行曲<br />\n香港人<br />\n虛作無聲<br />\n暴徒<br />\n自游<br />\n和你飛<br />\n我們都是這樣走過的<br />\n煲底之約<br />\n山下見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Will (not) see you soon</span> (莊正新歌）<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n假使世界原來不像你如期<br />\n願<br />\n十八<br />\n家明<br />\n雞蛋與羔羊<br />\n發現號<br />\n<del>無盡</del><br />\n<br />\n肥媽有話兒<br />\nfuck the popo<br />\n二零一九<br />\n惡世紀<br />\n揸緊中指<br />\n人話<br />\n<br />\n<del>今天我</del> 海闊天空<br />\n撐起雨傘<br />\n問誰未發聲/Do you hear the people sing<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n🏴"},{"pid":"37b4a9b1a9bf89e94b3e4ba803e08542f0c174c9","tid":1906083,"uid":92448,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"黃嘅歌手其實都要<br />\n填詞作曲又得"},{"pid":"2cb5e0ce8968e107b20cd95cabae711edaf9a3a2","tid":1906083,"uid":293967,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:37:21.000Z","msg":"漏左  有班警察毅進仔"},{"pid":"7a681e921e7b29c94876fa9d54079121a984f330","tid":1906083,"uid":104138,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"自行去youtube download<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n商業播歌要買版權，一係版權持有人授權，咪學足支那種侵權先得架"},{"pid":"1fa2571e9daa3d965cb8e2cf28f1512d838aad31","tid":1906083,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cb5e0ce8968e107b20cd95cabae711edaf9a3a2","tid":1906083,"uid":293967,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:37:21.000Z","msg":"漏左  有班警察毅進仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:38:07.000Z","msg":"太短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069b34e2f253bd06bcabd5ca11f80314c41ed0c5","tid":1906083,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:38:44.000Z","msg":"海報 文宣 memo紙<br />\n如果全部黃店都有呢d已經算好，手足唔洗貼得咁辛苦"},{"pid":"9df207501fc6ae64246998c6d49d7ba1c12f1d67","tid":1906083,"uid":5670,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:39:24.000Z","msg":"播係可以，但唔應該強制咁做。<br />\n<br />\n唔該唔好將個標準係咁拉高。"},{"pid":"acf2aa267b73b77d9cb1b68616c6448031d75404","tid":1906083,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"7a681e921e7b29c94876fa9d54079121a984f330","tid":1906083,"uid":104138,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"自行去youtube download<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face